---
// Hero principal de la home
---

<section
  class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6 overflow-hidden"
  style="background-color: #fefcff;"
>
  <!-- Dreamy Sky Pink Glow -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 z-0"
    style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 70%, rgba(173, 216, 230, 0.35), transparent 60%), radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.4), transparent 60%);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p
      class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest text-neutral-600 uppercase mb-4"
    >
      Agencia de Marketing Digital
    </p>
    <h1
      class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl tracking-tighter font-bold leading-tight mb-8 text-neutral-950"
    >
      Marcas que <span class="italic text-neutral-500">crecen</span><br />con
      propósito
    </h1>
    <p
      class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 text-pretty"
    >
      En Zarpa Creativa combinamos estrategia, creatividad y datos para que tu
      marca no solo aparezca, sino que conecte.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href="/servicios"
        class="inline-block bg-neutral-950 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-700 transition-colors"
      >
        Nuestros servicios
      </a>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block border border-neutral-950/20 text-neutral-950 font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-950/5 transition-colors"
      >
        Hablemos
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
